+- `php -l wordpress/smc-superfib-sniper/smc-superfib-sniper.php`: PASS (no syntax errors).
+- `php -l wordpress/smc-superfib-sniper/class-market-data-service.php`: PASS (no syntax errors).
+- PHP test loop: `set +e; pass=0; fail=0; while IFS= read -r f; do php "$f"; status=$?; if [ $status -eq 0 ]; then pass=$((pass + 1)); else fail=$((fail + 1)); fi; done < <(find wordpress/smc-superfib-sniper/tests/php -maxdepth 1 -type f -name '*.php' | sort); echo "pass=$pass fail=$fail"`: 23 passing files, 2 failing files in this environment. Failures observed: `test-mt5-snapshot-contract.php` (`AOV_EQUILIBRIUM_ZONE` expected, `CANDLES_STALE` actual) and `test-progressive-lot-sizing.php` (GBPUSD e1 lot expected `0.28`, actual `0`).
